        {
          "scid": "an5.35:1.1",
          "pli": "“Pañcime, bhikkhave, dāne ānisaṃsā. ",
          "en": "“Mendicants, there are five benefits of giving. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:1.2",
          "pli": "Katame pañca? ",
          "en": "What five? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:1.3",
          "pli": "Bahuno janassa piyo hoti manāpo; ",
          "en": "A giver, a donor is dear and beloved by many people. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:1.4",
          "pli": "santo sappurisā bhajanti; ",
          "en": "Good people associate with them. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:1.5",
          "pli": "kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggacchati; ",
          "en": "They get a good reputation. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:1.6",
          "pli": "gihidhammā anapagato hoti; ",
          "en": "They don’t neglect a layperson’s duties. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:1.7",
          "pli": "kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjati. ",
          "en": "When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:1.8",
          "pli": "Ime kho, bhikkhave, pañca dāne ānisaṃsāti. ",
          "en": "These are the five benefits of giving. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:2.1",
          "pli": "Dadamāno piyo hoti, ",
          "en": "Giving, one is loved, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:2.2",
          "pli": "sataṃ dhammaṃ anukkamaṃ; ",
          "en": "and follows the way of the good. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:2.3",
          "pli": "Santo naṃ sadā bhajanti, ",
          "en": "The good, disciplined spiritual practitioners "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:2.4",
          "pli": "saññatā brahmacārayo. ",
          "en": "associate with you. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:3.1",
          "pli": "Te tassa dhammaṃ desenti, ",
          "en": "They teach you the Dhamma "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:3.2",
          "pli": "Sabbadukkhāpanūdanaṃ; ",
          "en": "that dispels all suffering. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:3.3",
          "pli": "Yaṃ so dhammaṃ idhaññāya, ",
          "en": "Understanding this teaching, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:3.4",
          "pli": "Parinibbāti anāsavo”ti. ",
          "en": "you’re extinguished without defilements.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an5.35:3.5",
          "pli": "Pañcamaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
